00:03:03.780 --> 00:03:07.320
there's pip compile, there's PDM, there's Rai.

00:03:08.060 --> 00:03:13.520
You need to use a tool and pin your dependency tree, because then you can see when there's

00:03:13.740 --> 00:03:19.840
updates, and you can update them deliberately and test and adapt to those changes.

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:24.580
